  <summary date="2025-01-30T13:55:54Z" status="Introduced in House">Baby Changing on Board Act

This bill requires Amtrak passenger rail trains to have a baby changing table in each Americans with Disabilities Act of 1990-compliant&#160;restroom.&#160;The bill applies to passenger rail trains that are (1) owned and operated by Amtrak, and (2) solicited for purchase after the bill's enactment&#160;for use by Amtrak.</summary>
